Steps to Reproduce:
1. Create an interface which has a property of a type which uses a generic in its signature
2. Subsequent code is incorrectly highlighted, presumably due to angle brackets being interpreted as JSX

Example code:

```
interface Test<T> {
    test: T;
}

interface Props {
    prop: Test<T>;
}

class Whatever {
}
```

